    <section id="sponsorship-info">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Support the Future of Local Talent</h2>
            <p>At Abuja Indigenous Talent Hunt, we are dedicated to discovering, nurturing, and promoting the rich talents of the indigenous people of Abuja, FCT, Nigeria. By becoming a sponsor, you can play a vital role in empowering young entrepreneurs, craftsmen, and artists to achieve their dreams and showcase their skills to a wider audience.</p>

            <h2>Why Sponsor Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Visibility:</strong> Gain exposure for your brand through our platform, social media channels, and events.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Impact:</strong> Contribute to the growth and development of local talent and the economy.</li>
                <li><strong>Networking Opportunities:</strong> Connect with other sponsors, industry leaders, and emerging talents.</li>
                <li><strong>Brand Alignment:</strong> Align your brand with creativity, innovation, and social responsibility.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Sponsorship Levels</h2>
            <p>We offer a range of sponsorship opportunities to suit different budgets and goals. Choose the level that’s right for you:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Platinum Sponsor:</strong> Exclusive title sponsorship, prominent logo placement, and speaking opportunities at events.</li>
                <li><strong>Gold Sponsor:</strong> High visibility on our platform, logo placement on promotional materials, and event participation.</li>
                <li><strong>Silver Sponsor:</strong> Logo placement on our website and social media, and recognition in event materials.</li>
                <li><strong>Bronze Sponsor:</strong> Acknowledgment on our website and social media, with options for tailored benefits.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How to Become a Sponsor</h2>
            <p>Ready to make a difference? Becoming a sponsor is easy. Simply follow these steps:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:sponsorship@talenthuntabuja.com">sponsorship@talenthuntabuja.com</a> to express your interest.</li>
                <li>Discuss your sponsorship goals with our team and choose the level that best fits your needs.</li>
                <li>Complete the sponsorship agreement and submit your payment.</li>
                <li>Receive your sponsorship package and start enjoying the benefits of being part of Abuja Talent Hunt.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our sponsorship opportunities, please don’t hesitate to reach out. We are here to help you make the most of your partnership with Abuja Indigenous Talent Hunt.</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:sponsorship@talenthuntabuja.com">sponsorship@talenthuntabuja.com</a></p>
